Memory: 4kb ram
Display: 64x32 monochrome
Program counter
16-bit index register (I): Points to locations in memory
Stack for 16-bit addresses, used for subroutines etc
8-bit delay timer, decrements 60 times/s
8-bit sound timer, beeps when not 0, decs 60t/s
16 8-bit variable registers, V0-VF
  * VF is also the flag register.

Keypad is like this:   First could be impl. like this:
123C    0123           1234
456D OR 4567           qwer
789E    89AB           asdf
A0BF    CDEF           zxcv
